rd-default card\" href=\"https:\/\/breakmedia.lndo.site\/work\/hugo\/\">\n      <div class=\"uk-card-media-top\" style=\"background-image: url('https:\/\/breakmedia.lndo.site\/app\/uploads\/2022\/03\/hugo-1.png')\"><\/div>\n      <div class=\"description uk-width-1-1 uk-visible@s\">\n        <div class=\"logo\">\n          <img src=https:\/\/breakmedia.lndo.site\/app\/uploads\/2022\/03\/hugo-logo-1.svg>\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"content\">\n          <h3>Wealthcare In Singapore.<\/h3>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n      <div class=\"description-mobile uk-width-1-1 uk-hidden@s\">\n        <div class=\"logo\">\n          <img src=https:\/\/breakmedia.lndo.site\/app\/uploads\/2022\/03\/hugo-logo-1.svg>\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"content\">\n          <h3>Wealthcare In Singapore.<\/h3>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/a>\n  <\/div>\n\n      <\/div>\n  \n<\/div>\n\n<div  class=\"uk-width-1-1 value-prop-and-subsection-and-image uk-position-relative content-image-module bg--neutral padding remove-\" uk-scrollspy=\"target: .animate-element; cls: uk-animation-slide-bottom-medium; delay: 200\">\n  <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n    <div uk-grid class=\"uk-grid uk-flex-between mb-80 animate-element\">\n            <div class=\"uk-child-width-1-1 width-45@m uk-width-2-5@l\">\n        <h2>BREAKING AND REBUILDING THE AGENCY MODEL.<\/h2>\n      <\/div>\n                  <div class=\"richtext-content uk-child-width-1-1 width-55@m\">\n        <p>We are an independent communications agency, established in 2019. We believe it\u2019s time to be better partners for our clients. Our vision is to break, and re-build an out-of- date agency model. We don\u2019t want to talk about our approach to planning communications. We want to understand your business challenges, and figure out how we can help. Our vision is to design lean, agile and effective teams around the specific needs of each individual client. We won\u2019t inflate your costs with high overheads and overpaid senior members of staff.<\/p>\n<p><strong>We are genuine and transparent in everything that we do, and want to achieve transformational results through real partnerships.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n      <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"image mb-80 animate-element\">\n      <img src=\"https:\/\/breakmedia.lndo.site\/app\/uploads\/2022\/03\/homepage-image-1.png\" alt=\"BREAKING AND REBUILDING THE AGENCY MODEL.\" class=\"visible@1440\">\n      <img src=\"https:\/\/breakmedia.lndo.site\/app\/uploads\/2022\/03\/homepage-image-small-screen.png\" alt=\"BREAKING AND REBUILDING THE AGENCY MODEL.\" class=\"uk-visible@s hidden@1440\">\n      <img src=\"https:\/\/breakmedia.lndo.site\/app\/uploads\/2022\/03\/homepage-image-mobile.png\" alt=\"BREAKING AND REBUILDING THE AGENCY MODEL.\" class=\"uk-hidden@s\">\n    <\/div>\n    \n    <div  class=\"lower-section\">\n      <div uk-grid class=\"uk-grid uk-flex-between mb-80 animate-element\">\n                <div class=\"uk-child-width-1-1 width-45@m uk-width-2-5@l\">\n          <h2>HOW WE WORK.<\/h2>\n        <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"richtext-content uk-child-width-1-1 width-55@m\">\n          <p>We have lean teams that can deliver all digital marketing services for our clients. We allocate the best talent, for the best price, based on what you need. Most of all, we want to get away from the jargon, and acronyms that overcomplicate advertising. You\u2019ll get straight honest answers, and clear business results.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #62b6cb;\"><strong>Here\u2019s what we do.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n        <\/div>\n              <\/div>\n\n      <div uk-grid class=\"uk-grid uk-grid-row-small uk-child-width-1-1 uk-child-width-1-3@s column--3\">\n                                    <div class=\"subsection animate-element\">\n            <div class=\"subsection-num mb-25\">1<\/div>\n            <div class=\"richtext-content\">\n              <p>We start by listening, focusing on your challenges, genuinely getting a handle on how marketing can help.<\/p>\n\n            <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                            <div class=\"subsection animate-element\">\n            <div class=\"subsection-num mb-25\">2<\/div>\n            <div class=\"richtext-content\">\n              <p>We research \u2013 using bespoke access to data and consumer panels, to show you clearly how advertising can deliver growth.<\/p>\n\n            <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                            <div class=\"subsection animate-element\">\n            <div class=\"subsection-num mb-25\">3<\/div>\n            <div class=\"richtext-content\">\n              <p>We set up the right strategy and team that will deliver results focused, data-driven advertising; maximising your return.<\/p>\n\n            <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n              <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n  <div class=\"bg-image uk-position-absolute\" style=\"background-image: url(https:\/\/breakmedia.lndo.site\/app\/uploads\/2022\/03\/tropical-silhoutte.png);\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div  class=\"uk-width-1-1 about-us-slider uk-position-relative bg--neutral padding remove-bottom\" style=\"background-image:url(https:\/\/breakmedia.lndo.site\/app\/uploads\/2022\/03\/bg-about-us.png);\">\n    <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                <h2 class=\"mb-80\" uk-scrollspy=\"cls: uk-animation-slide-bottom-medium; delay: 100;\">ABOUT US.<\/h2>\n        \n                <div class=\"outer-slider\">\n            <ul class=\"slide-items\">\n                                                <li class=\"slide-0 uk-flex\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-grid\" uk-grid>\n                        <div class=\"uk-width-1-1 width-43@m\" uk-scrollspy=\"cls: uk-animation-slide-bottom-medium; target: .animate-element; delay: 100;\">\n                            <div class=\"content-column animate-element\">\n                                <h3 class=\"uk-margin-small-bottom\">CHARLIE NEWBERY<\/h3>\n                                <p class=\"subheader uk-margin-remove-top mb-40\">FOUNDING PARTNER<\/p>\n                                <div class=\"richtext-content\">\n                                    <p>Charlie has over 15 years of experience, leading global clients in London, Dubai, Hong Kong and Singapore. He was most recently APAC Chief Media Officer for Digitas, an integrated full service agency headquartered in Singapore.\u200b<\/p>\n<p>His most recent key accounts were Samsung, Pan Pacific Hotels, Shangri La Hotels, Hewlett Packard Enterprise, &amp; Visa. During his time at Digitas, he dedicated himself to powering innovation through the smart use of new technologies and data. Key to his success was working closely with creative, data, and technology teams, to create highly personalized and engaging experiences.<\/p>\n\n                                <\/div>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"image-column uk-text-center uk-text-right@m uk-width-1-1 width-57@m uk-position-relative\" uk-scrollspy=\"cls: uk-animation-slide-right-small; target: .animate-element; delay: 500;\">\n                            <img class=\"animate-element\" src=\"https:\/\/breakmedia.lndo.site\/app\/uploads\/2022\/04\/charlie.png\" alt=\"CHARLIE NEWBERY\">\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/li>    \n                                                <li class=\"slide-1 uk-flex\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-grid\" uk-grid>\n                        <div class=\"uk-width-1-1 width-43@m\" uk-scrollspy=\"cls: uk-animation-slide-bottom-medium; target: .animate-element; delay: 100;\">\n                            <div class=\"content-column animate-element\">\n                                <h3 class=\"uk-margin-small-bottom\">BEN MCANENY<\/h3>\n                                <p class=\"subheader uk-margin-remove-top mb-40\">FOUNDING PARTNER<\/p>\n                                <div class=\"richtext-content\">\n                                    <p>Ben has over 10 years\u2019 experience as a Digital media professional, leading both regional and global strategy &amp; activation, across several continents. Throughout his career, he has been responsible for leading campaigns for some of the worlds largest brands, across both Digital and Traditional media.<\/p>\n<p>Initially, he stared as a performance specialist, working at the UKs largest independent performance agencies, where he was the global agency performance lead for Brands such as Nespresso and Mercedes Benz. During this period, he gained a vast experience across multiple verticals, ranging from Travel, Luxury products, Ecommerce, and B2B Tech.<\/p>\n\n                                <\/div>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"image-column uk-text-center uk-text-right@m uk-width-1-1 width-57@m uk-position-relative\" uk-scrollspy=\"cls: uk-animation-slide-right-small; target: .animate-element; delay: 500;\">\n                            <img class=\"animate-element\" src=\"https:\/\/breakmedia.lndo.site\/app\/uploads\/2022\/04\/ben.png\" alt=\"BEN MCANENY\">\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/li>    \n                            <\/ul>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div uk-slider class=\"slider\">\n            <div class=\"uk-slider-container uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"slide-nav-mobile uk-position-absolute\">\n                    <a class=\"slide-nav uk-slidenav-large uk-position-relative uk-padding-remove uk-hidden@s\" href=\"#\" uk-slidenav-previous uk-slider-item=\"previous\" uk-scrollspy=\"cls: uk-animation-fade; delay: 500;\"><\/a>\n                    <a class=\"slide-nav uk-slidenav-large uk-position-relative uk-padding-remove uk-hidden@s\" href=\"#\" uk-slidenav-next uk-slider-item=\"next\"  uk-scrollspy=\"cls: uk